/* Lucario / Milotic / Garchomp). Moves, items, abilities, levels all match */
/* Sinnoh Stadium exactly. EV/IV constraint per BDSP roll table: every mon */
/* spends all 510 EVs with at least one stat at 252; every mon except */
/* Spiritomb has 31 IVs in five stats and 0 IVs in one stat. Spiritomb is */
/* the lone full-31 outlier. The 0-IV stat is always the attacking stat */
/* the mon never uses, paired with a nature that drops the same stat for */
/* a stacked confusion/Foul-Play hedge. */
