/* v0.53.2 — Legends Arceus trainers. User-provided canonical rosters. */
/* EV conversion: PLA's "Effort Levels" (0-10) map to modern EVs via */
/* EL × 25.2, then total scaled down to fit the 510-EV cap. For "all-equal" */
/* spreads at EL 5/7/10, this works out to a flat 85/85/85/85/85/85 (510). */
/* For varied spreads (e.g. Adaman's Leafeon at 7/7/7/7/7/10), the unique */
/* stat gets proportionally more (~117 vs 79). Volo's Togekiss has EL 1 */
/* across the board per user spec = ~25 each (under cap, kept literal). */
/* Volo's other mons have no EL listed in user spec, so they default to */
/* 0 EVs (Volo's LA stats are intentionally low-trained — that's accurate). */
/* IVs follow BDSP convention: 31 in five stats, 0 in the unused attacking */
/* stat (pure physical = 0 SpA, pure special = 0 Atk); mixed mons keep */
/* full 31s. Abilities chosen competitively since PLA mons don't carry */
/* abilities — Pressure/Natural Cure/Serene Grace/Intimidate/Magic Guard etc. */

